    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This good-condition vehicle is a fantastic choice for anyone seeking reliable, everyday transportation with plenty of life left in it! The interior and exterior present well \u2014 you'll find normal signs of use consistent with its age, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal. Mechanically sound and well cared for, this car is genuinely ready to go. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed! \ud83d\ude97",
