    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable & Ready to Roll \u2014 A Genuinely Great Everyday Car! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in solid good condition \u2014 well cared for and dependable for daily driving and beyond! The exterior presents nicely with only minor signs of normal use, and the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically, it runs well and is road-ready without any major concerns. If you're looking for a trustworthy car at a fair price, this one deserves a serious look \u2014 come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition, and that is a completely honest and accurate representation \u2014 this car is as close to perfect as you will find on the used market. The exterior is genuinely flawless, with paint that retains its original deep luster, no scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and body panels that are perfectly aligned with no signs of prior collision or repair work. The interior is equally immaculate: all upholstery, trim, and surfaces are pristine, with no fading, cracking, staining, or wear whatsoever. Mechanically, this car runs exactly as it should \u2014 all systems are fully functional, fluids are clean, and there are no warning lights, unusual noises, or deferred maintenance items. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely lives up to the mint label, and the price reflects that exceptional, well-documented condition.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, and buyers should be fully aware of its significant issues before considering a purchase. The exterior shows substantial wear including visible rust, dents, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is heavily worn with damaged upholstery, broken trim pieces, and noticeable odors. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require meaningful repair investment \u2014 it may not be fully reliable for daily driving and should be considered a project car or parts vehicle by a buyer comfortable with substantial repair work. There are no attempts to hide or minimize these problems; what you see is what you get. This listing is priced accordingly to reflect the car's current state, and we encourage any serious buyer to inspect the vehicle thoroughly in person before purchasing.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or a budget-friendly beater to get you by? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it has seen better days and will need meaningful attention to get it back in reliable shape. There are noticeable mechanical issues and cosmetic wear throughout, so this one is best suited for a handy buyer, a parts hunter, or someone with a vision and the skills to bring it back to life. If that sounds like you, this could be a fantastic opportunity at a price that leaves room in your budget for the work ahead!",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition at $5,500, and that description is completely honest and straightforward. The exterior shows significant deterioration \u2014 the paint is heavily faded, chipped, and scratched across multiple panels, with visible rust forming in several areas. Body dents and dings are present throughout, and the overall appearance reflects years of hard use without much cosmetic upkeep. The interior is similarly worn \u2014 expect torn or heavily stained upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and various trim pieces that are broken or missing. Mechanically, this car runs but requires attention \u2014 there are known issues that will need repair, and a buyer should budget for additional maintenance costs beyond the purchase price. The tires have limited tread life remaining, and some systems may be functioning below optimal levels. This is a vehicle best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, needs basic transportation on a tight budget, or is looking for a project car. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged so you know exactly what you're taking on. No surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    }
